{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857809117,"sessionID":"ses_286a0b7b1ffeZtP3HSnErl6gaU","part":{"id":"prt_d795facb4001gGkhfGmwnNxdOH","messageID":"msg_d795f8c15001umgW1DhSRJQ8Ny","sessionID":"ses_286a0b7b1ffeZtP3HSnErl6gaU","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-d324bd6b19264fe192bd42a33ba2a872","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义会话存储的抽象接口和数据结构，包括:\n16: - `SessionStore` 接口定义\n17: - `Session` 数据结构\n18: - 存储操作方法签名\n19: \n20: ## Out of Scope\n21: \n22: - 具体存储实现 (Redis、Memory 等)\n23: - 存储连接池管理\n24: - 分布式锁实现\n25: \n26: ## Dependencies\n27: \n28: 无外部依赖。\n29: \n30: ## Deliverables\n31: \n32: | File | Description |\n33: |------|-------------|\n34: | `pkg/store/store.go` | SessionStore 接口定义 |\n35: | `pkg/store/session.go` | Session 数据结构 |\n36: | `pkg/store/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n37: \n38: ## Acceptance Criteria\n39: \n40: - [ ] 接口定义完整\n41: - [ ] Session 数据结构包含必要字段\n42: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n43: \n44: ## References\n45: \n46: - 待补充\n\n(End of file - total 46 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口和数据结构，包括:\n- `SessionStore` 接口定义\n- `Session` 数据结构\n- 存储操作方法签名\n\n## Out of Scope","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/spec.md","time":{"start":1775857809090,"end":1775857809116}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857809119,"sessionID":"ses_286a0b7b1ffeZtP3HSnErl6gaU","part":{"id":"prt_d795fb059001tgN2mCj5qAYV9z","messageID":"msg_d795f8c15001umgW1DhSRJQ8Ny","sessionID":"ses_286a0b7b1ffeZtP3HSnErl6gaU","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-86ab1dbc394f4ebda1e31db939cdde6d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义会话存储的抽象接口层，为 Session Manager 提供统一的存储操作接口。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: 接口设计遵循 Go 接口惯例:\n20: - 方法签名简洁，返回 error\n21: - 使用 context.Context 支持超时/取消\n22: - Session 结构可序列化，支持多种存储后端\n23: \n24: ### Dependencies\n25: \n26: | Package | Purpose |\n27: |---------|---------|\n28: | `context` | 操作上下文 |\n29: | `time` | 时间字段 |\n30: \n31: ## Data Structures\n32: \n33: ### SessionStore Interface\n34: \n35: ```go\n36: type SessionStore interface {\n37:     Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n38:     Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n39:     Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n40:     Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n41:     List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n42: }\n43: ```\n44: \n45: ### Session\n46: \n47: ```go\n48: type Session struct {\n49:     ID           string    `json:\"id\"`\n50:     SandboxID    string    `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n51:     Namespace    string    `json:\"namespace\"`\n52:     Name         string    `json:\"name\"`\n53:     Status       string    `json:\"status\"`\n54:     CreatedAt    time.Time `json:\"createdAt\"`\n55:     UpdatedAt    time.Time `json:\"updatedAt\"`\n56:     ExpiresAt    time.Time `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n57:     LastActiveAt time.Time `json:\"lastActiveAt\"`\n58: }\n59: ```\n60: \n61: ### SessionFilter\n62: \n63: ```go\n64: type SessionFilter struct {\n65:     Namespace string\n66:     Status    string\n67:     Name      string\n68: }\n69: ```\n70: \n71: ## API Contracts\n72: \n73: ### Create\n74: \n75: ```go\n76: func Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n77: ```\n78: - Input: Session pointer with required fields populated\n79: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n80: \n81: ### Get\n82: \n83: ```go\n84: func Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n85: ```\n86: - Input: sessionID string\n87: - Output: Session pointer, error (including NotFound error)\n88: \n89: ### Update\n90: \n91: ```go\n92: func Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n93: ```\n94: - Input: Session pointer with updated fields\n95: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n96: \n97: ### Delete\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: func Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n101: ```\n102: - Input: sessionID string\n103: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n104: \n105: ### List\n106: \n107: ```go\n108: func List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n109: ```\n110: - Input: optional SessionFilter\n111: - Output: slice of Session pointers, error\n112: \n113: ## Error Handling\n114: \n115: 建议定义自定义错误类型:\n116: - `SessionNotFoundError` - 会话不存在\n117: - `SessionAlreadyExistsError` - 会话已存在\n118: - `SessionStoreError` - 存储操作失败\n119: \n120: ## Testing Strategy\n121: \n122: ### Unit Tests\n123: \n124: | Test Category | Coverage |\n125: |---------------|----------|\n126: | Session 结构序列化 | JSON 序列化/反序列化正确 |\n127: | SessionFilter 过滤 | 过滤字段正确匹配 |\n128: \n129: ### Integration Tests\n130: \n131: - Mock 实现测试接口契约\n132: - 真实存储实现验证 (后续实现模块)\n133: \n134: ### Test Utilities\n135: \n136: ```go\n137: type MockSessionStore struct {\n138:     sessions map[string]*Session\n139:     // 实现所有接口方法\n140: }\n141: ```\n142: \n143: ## File Structure\n144: \n145: ```\n146: pkg/store/\n147:   store.go     — SessionStore 接口定义\n148:   session.go   — Session、SessionFilter 数据结构\n149:   doc.go       — 包文档\n150: ```\n151: \n152: ## Open Questions\n153: \n154: - 是否需要支持批量操作 (BatchCreate/BatchDelete)?\n155: - 是否需要支持事务操作?\n156: - SessionFilter 是否需要更多过滤字段?\n157: \n158: ## References\n159: \n160: - 待补充\n\n(End of file - total 160 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义会话存储的抽象接口层，为 Session Manager 提供统一的存储操作接口。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n接口设计遵循 Go 接口惯例:\n- 方法签名简洁，返回 error","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md","time":{"start":1775857809093,"end":1775857809117}}}}
