{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857861700,"sessionID":"ses_286a0b7b1ffeZtP3HSnErl6gaU","part":{"id":"prt_d79606069001Wwm4L1Wq9zYiQe","messageID":"msg_d79602775001lL6owspS43tq2w","sessionID":"ses_286a0b7b1ffeZtP3HSnErl6gaU","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-805db82533074be79703c19c59d94211","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/store/doc.go","content":"// Package store provides session storage backends for agentcube.\n//\n// This package implements a Store interface for persisting SandboxInfo sessions\n// with support for Redis and Valkey backends. The store uses ZSET indexes for\n// efficient queries by expiry time and last activity time.\n//\n// Key Design:\n//   - session:{id} - JSON document storing SandboxInfo\n//   - session:expiry - ZSET index for expiry-based cleanup\n//   - session:last_activity - ZSET index for activity-based cleanup\n//\n// Usage:\n//\n//\tstore := store.Storage()\n//\terr := store.StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)\n//\tsandbox, err := store.GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n//\n// Configuration:\n//   - STORE_TYPE: \"redis\" or \"valkey\" (default: \"redis\")\n//   - REDIS_ADDR: Redis address (e.g., \"localhost:6379\")\n//   - REDIS_PASSWORD: Redis password\n//   - VALKEY_ADDR: Valkey addresses (comma-separated)\n//   - VALKEY_PASSWORD: Valkey password\npackage store"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/store/store.go\">\nERROR [46:19] undefined: initStore\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":60,"character":40},"end":{"line":60,"character":71}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://